    Backup additional resources (#5224)
    
    Add additional resources to the backup as follows:
    
    1. rolebindings - users a allowed to create role binding for their
    service account. In addition, in clusters that doesn't use kubesaw,
    rolebindings are used for granting permissions to users.
    
    2. imagerepositories - the ImageRepository resources is created
    by the UI when onboarding a new component, thus it should be backed
    up as well.
    
    3. repositories - the Tekton repository resource is created by the
    build service if the component doesn't have the "build.appstudio.openshift.io/status"
    annotation. Since the components in the back have this annotation,
    the build service won't create the repository resources after restoring
    the components, thus the repository resource should be backed up as well.
    
    4. release resources - those are core Konflux resources thus they
    should be backed up as well.
    
    Signed-off-by: Gal Ben Haim <gbenhaim@redhat.com>

